    <teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Memorandum by the British Prime Minister (
                        Attlee
                    ) to President Truman
                    
                    Copy obtained from the Harry S. Truman Library,
                        Independence, Mo.</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1945v08</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d700</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">700</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1945-07-31T00:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1945-07-31T23:59:59-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-07-31T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-07-31T00:00:00-05:00" n="700" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d700">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">Truman Papers</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by the British Prime Minister</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Attlee</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to President <persName type="to">Truman</persName>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="11" xml:id="d700fn11">Copy obtained from the Harry S. Truman Library,
                        Independence, Mo.</note>
                </head>
                <p>I have read your memorandum of July 24 about Palestine. You will I am sure
                    understand that I cannot give you any statement on policy until we have had time
                    to consider the matter, and this is simply to inform you that we will give early
                    and careful consideration to your memorandum.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>C. R. <hi rend="smallcaps">Attlee</hi>
                    </signed>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-07-31">31 July,
                            1945</date>.</dateline>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
</TEI>
